<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>

    <ThingDef ParentName="BasePawn">
      <defName>TW_Mech_Capitalistic_Militor</defName>
      <label>资本家小镰</label>
      <description>这台镀铬的机械族商人挂着永不熄灭的电子微笑，游走于各个殖民地之间，兜售一种它称之为“镰口贸易”的“双赢”业务——当然，赢的总是它。支付足够的钢铁，它就会“慷慨”地带着几名助手加入你的殖民地，并确保你明白“人力（尤其是机械大学生）是最宝贵的可再生资源”。它的核心处理器里只运行着一条指令：利润最大化。</description>
      <statBases>
            <MoveSpeed>4</MoveSpeed>
            <Flammability>0</Flammability>
            <ComfyTemperatureMin>-100</ComfyTemperatureMin>
            <ComfyTemperatureMax>1000</ComfyTemperatureMax>
            <PsychicSensitivity>0</PsychicSensitivity>
            <StaggerDurationFactor>0</StaggerDurationFactor>
            <ToxicResistance>1</ToxicResistance>
            <ArmorRating_Blunt>0.2</ArmorRating_Blunt>
            <ArmorRating_Sharp>1.5</ArmorRating_Sharp>
            <ArmorRating_Heat>2</ArmorRating_Heat>
      </statBases>
      <race>
	    <hideTrainingTab>true</hideTrainingTab>
		<thinkTreeMain>Capitalistic_Militors_ThinkTreeMain</thinkTreeMain>
		<thinkTreeConstant>Capitalistic_Militors_ThinkTreeConstant</thinkTreeConstant>
            <intelligence>ToolUser</intelligence>
            <isImmuneToInfections>true</isImmuneToInfections>
            <needsRest>false</needsRest>
            <hasGenders>false</hasGenders>
		    <foodType>None</foodType>
            <hasCorpse>true</hasCorpse>
            <lifeExpectancy>1000</lifeExpectancy>
            <soundMeleeDodge>Pawn_MeleeDodge</soundMeleeDodge>
            <soundCallIntervalRange>120~240</soundCallIntervalRange>
		    <body>Mech_Light</body>
            <baseBodySize>1</baseBodySize>
		    <baseHealthScale>1</baseHealthScale>
			<fleshType>Mechanoid</fleshType>
	      <bloodDef>Filth_MachineBits</bloodDef>
		      <renderTree>Animal</renderTree>
        <lifeStageAges>
          <li>
            <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
            <minAge>0</minAge>
            <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Wounded</soundWounded>
            <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Death</soundDeath>
            <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Call</soundCall>
          </li>
          <li>
            <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
            <minAge>100</minAge>
            <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Wounded</soundWounded>
            <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Death</soundDeath>
            <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_Militor_Call</soundCall>
          </li>
        </lifeStageAges>
      </race>
	  <comps>
			<li Class="NCL.CompProperties_Trader">
				<traderDefName>Mechanoid_Employer</traderDefName>
			</li>
			<li Class="NCL.CompProperties_MechEmployable">
				<silverPerDay>200</silverPerDay>
			</li>
			<li Class="NCL.CompProperties_AllDead">
				<toggleLabelKey>NCL.FireAllUniversityStudents</toggleLabelKey>
				<toggleDescKey>NCL.FireAllUniversityStudentsDesc</toggleDescKey>
				<toggleIconPath>ModIcon/YouAreFired</toggleIconPath>
				<unableKey>NCL.CanNotFireAllUniversityStudents</unableKey>
				<mechanoidToKill>TW_University_Minitor</mechanoidToKill>
			</li>
			<li Class="NCL.CompProperties_SkillRefresh">
				<targetPawnDefs>
                <li>TW_University_Minitor</li> <!-- 必须完全匹配目标生物Def -->
				</targetPawnDefs>
				<checkIntervalTicks>3000</checkIntervalTicks>
			</li>
      </comps>
		<butcherProducts>
			<Silver>5000</Silver>
		</butcherProducts>
    </ThingDef>
  
    <PawnKindDef ParentName="LightMechanoidKind">
      <defName>TW_Mech_Capitalistic_Militor</defName>
      <label>资本家小镰</label>
    <allowInMechClusters>false</allowInMechClusters>
      <race>TW_Mech_Capitalistic_Militor</race>
      <description>这台镀铬的机械族商人挂着永不熄灭的电子微笑，游走于各个殖民地之间，兜售一种它称之为“镰口贸易”的“双赢”业务——当然，赢的总是它。支付足够的钢铁，它就会“慷慨”地带着几名助手加入你的殖民地，并确保你明白“人力（尤其是机械大学生）是最宝贵的可再生资源”。它的核心处理器里只运行着一条指令：利润最大化。</description>
      <defaultFactionType>NCL_faction</defaultFactionType>
      <combatPower>45</combatPower>
    <immuneToTraps>true</immuneToTraps>
      <lifeStages>
        <li>
          <bodyGraphicData>
			<texPath>Races/Capital</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
            <drawSize>1.25</drawSize>
            <shadowData>
              <volume>(0.3, 0.4, 0.3)</volume>
              <offset>(0,0,-0.25)</offset>
            </shadowData>
          </bodyGraphicData>
        </li>
        <li>
          <bodyGraphicData>
            <texPath>Races/Capital</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
            <drawSize>1.25</drawSize>
            <shadowData>
              <volume>(0.3, 0.4, 0.3)</volume>
              <offset>(0,0,-0.25)</offset>
            </shadowData>
          </bodyGraphicData>
        </li>
      </lifeStages>
      <abilities>
			<li>Call_for_University_Students</li>
       </abilities>
    </PawnKindDef>
	
	
	<ThingDef Name="TW_University_Minitor" ParentName="LightMechanoid" Abstract="True">
		<description>这群可怜的铁皮苦力是殖民地真正的劳动力，被资本家小镰以“实习机会”和“福报”的名义骗来，承担所有挖矿、搬运、清洁甚至充当人肉沙袋的脏活累活。它们的外壳上总是布满刮痕，光学镜头因长期过劳而闪烁不定，但资本家小镰坚称这是“成长的代价”。（警告：长期高压工作可能导致它们突然崩溃，届时不听话者将突然化为”自愿离职报告“。）</description>
		<race>
        <lifeStageAges>
          <li>
            <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
            <minAge>0</minAge>
            <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Wounded</soundWounded>
            <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Death</soundDeath>
            <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Call</soundCall>
          </li>
          <li>
            <def>MechanoidFullyFormed</def>
            <minAge>100</minAge>
            <soundWounded>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Wounded</soundWounded>
            <soundDeath>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Death</soundDeath>
            <soundCall>Pawn_Mech_WarUrchin_Call</soundCall>
          </li>
        </lifeStageAges>
        <thinkTreeConstant>MechConstant</thinkTreeConstant>
		<mechEnabledWorkTypes>   		
		<li>BasicWorker</li>
		<li>Firefighter</li> 
		</mechEnabledWorkTypes>
		<mechFixedSkillLevel>10</mechFixedSkillLevel>	
        <baseHealthScale>1</baseHealthScale>	
      </race>
	  <comps Inherit="False">
		<li Class="CompProperties_CanBeDormant" />
        <li Class="CompProperties_WakeUpDormant">
          <wakeUpOnDamage>true</wakeUpOnDamage>
          <wakeUpCheckRadius>300</wakeUpCheckRadius>
          <wakeUpSound>MechanoidsWakeUp</wakeUpSound>
        </li>
      </comps>		
    </ThingDef>

    <PawnKindDef Name="TW_University_Minitor_PawnkindBase" ParentName="LightMechanoidKind" Abstract="True">
      <allowInMechClusters>false</allowInMechClusters>
	  <isFighter>false</isFighter>	<!-- should not be in raids now?-->
      <forceNoDeathNotification>true</forceNoDeathNotification>
    </PawnKindDef>
	
	
